name: SURVIVE, BABY WHALE!
description:
feed the hungry baby whale. However, if whale eat more than five microplastics, the baby whale dies.

-The way to remove the game rule  is to press q again.

-When a player eats food, it makes a sound.

-The game has an ending. If you eat food, you can see the ending.
